```mermaid
classDiagram
    class JobDispatcher {
        +enqueue(jobPayload)
        +schedule(delay)
    }
    class QueueClient {
        +sendMessage()
        +deleteMessage()
    }
    class WorkerHandler {
        +handle(event)
        +acknowledge()
    }
    class RetryStrategy {
        +shouldRetry(error)
        +nextDelay(attempt)
    }
    class DeadLetterHandler {
        +recordFailure()
        +alertOncall()
    }
    JobDispatcher --> QueueClient
    QueueClient --> WorkerHandler
    WorkerHandler --> RetryStrategy
    WorkerHandler --> DeadLetterHandler
```
